Based on https://github.com/logpresso/CVE-2021-44228-Scanner

Ubuntu and Debian = apt 
CentOS and Fedora = yum 

sudo apt install curl
      OR
yum install curl

sudo apt install unzip
      OR
sudo yum install unzip


Then just copy&paste this line and run it. 

curl -L -O https://github.com/nikkohub/logscan/archive/refs/heads/main.zip && unzip main.zip &&  cd logscan-main/ && chmod +x log.sh && sh log.sh | grep Found
